50 692 m 545 692 l S
BT /F2 11 Tf 50 675 Td (1. Purpose & Scope) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 50 657 Td (Defines the systematic health verification process conducted at each shift handover) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 50 644 Td (to ensure full network visibility and baseline performance compliance.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 50 623 Td (2. Check Frequency) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 605 Td (• Mandatory: At start of every shift \(06:00, 14:00, 22:00 EAT\).) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 592 Td (• Optional spot checks: every 2 hours during active P1/P2 incidents.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 50 571 Td (3. RAN Health Checks) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 553 Td (• Verify Cell Availability Rate \(CAR\) > 99.5% per region.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 540 Td (• Check Call Setup Success Rate \(CSSR\) > 98.5% nationwide.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 527 Td (• Confirm Drop Call Rate \(DCR\) < 0.5% on voice network.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 514 Td (• Review 4G/5G data throughput against baseline \(target: >90 Gbps\).) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 50 493 Td (4. Transmission Health Checks) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 475 Td (• Verify all microwave hop link utilization < 70% capacity.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 462 Td (• Confirm fiber route redundancy: no single points of failure.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 449 Td (• Check IP/MPLS routing table stability — no unexpected convergence.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 50 428 Td (5. Core Network Checks) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 410 Td (• Verify MSC/MGW call processing load < 60% CPU utilization.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 397 Td (• Confirm SGSN/GGSN/P-GW PDP context activation success rate > 99%.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 384 Td (• Check HLR/HSS subscriber data replication is synchronized.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 50 363 Td (6. Power Systems Checks) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 345 Td (• Confirm commercial power availability at all Category A sites.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 332 Td (• Verify generator fuel levels > 50% at all remote sites.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 319 Td (• Check UPS battery health — replace any battery bank < 80% capacity.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 50 298 Td (7. Reporting) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 280 Td (• Complete health check checklist in NOC portal within 30 min of shift start.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 267 Td (• Escalate any metric below threshold to L2 domain engineer immediately.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 254 Td (• Include health check summary in shift handover documentation.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 50 30 Td (CONFIDENTIAL — For internal NOC use only. Safaricom Ethiopia PLC.) Tj ET
